OL,3,CRoadworks carried out to fix 'optical
OL,4,Cillusion' cycle path
OL,6,FRoadworks to fix the "optical
OL,7,Fillusion", which causes people to trip
OL,8,Fon Keynsham High Street, are complete.
OL,10,FAround three people trip and hurt
OL,11,Fthemselves every month on the cycle
OL,12,Flane, which was installed in 2022.
OL,14,FEven after the cycle lane was painted
OL,15,Fred, the confusing kerbs and painted
OL,16,Flines on the street continued to
OL,17,Fcreate an "optical illusion" causing
OL,18,Fpeople to trip.
