OL,4,Cillusion' cycle path
OL,6,FBut Bath and North East Somerset
OL,7,FCouncil have now repainted the solid
OL,8,Fwhite line as a broken line, in the
OL,9,Fhopes this will stop the confusion and
OL,10,Fthe injuries. Double yellow lines have
OL,11,Falso been painted on the street.
OL,13,FLocals have been waiting over a month
OL,14,Fand a half for the work to happen
OL,15,Fafter Bath and North East Somerset
OL,16,FCouncil said in February it would
OL,17,Fhappen "at the earliest opportunity,"
OL,18,Fweather and contactor availability
OL,19,Fallowing.
