OL,6,FPaul Roper (Kingsmead, Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrat), the council's cabinet
OL,8,Fmember for economic and cultural
OL,9,Fsustainable development, said: "This
OL,10,Fmitigation should make the change in
OL,11,Flevels clearer to pedestrians and
OL,12,Fprevent further trips and falls.
OL,14,F"We are grateful for people's patience
OL,15,Fwhile the audit was undertaken and the
OL,16,Froad safety report compiled, which we
OL,17,Fare acting on."
