OL,6,FBut local councillor and the council's
OL,7,Fmember advocate for road safety Alan
OL,8,FHale (Keynsham South, Conservative)
OL,9,Fwarned in February that the changes
OL,10,Fplanned by the council are not those
OL,11,Fwhich auditors recommended.
OL,13,FThey had suggested putting tactile
OL,14,Fpaving along the kerb but the scheme's
OL,15,Fdesigners said this could cause more
OL,16,Fconfusion.
